enableOutTransfer.t.sol
├── when caller is not the risk manager timelock
│  └── it should revert with UnauthorizedCaller
└── when caller is the risk manager timelock
   ├── given no adapter for the provided bridge ID is registered in this contract
   │  └── it should revert with BridgeAdapterDoesNotExist
   └── given an adapter for the provided bridge ID is registered in this contract
      ├── given outgoing transfers are already enabled for the corresponding bridge
      │  └── it should revert with AlreadyEnabled
      └── given outgoing transfers are not already enabled for the corresponding bridge
         ├── it should enable outgoing transfers for the corresponding bridge
         └── it should emit an OutTransferEnabled event
